EverQuest price increase <br>
03/25/2002 <br>
<br>
Due to the increased costs of running the EverQuest game service, we will be increasing our subscription rates in April. Effective April 25, the new monthly subscription rate will be $12.95/month. We will continue to offer discounts from the new rate plan on multi-month subscriptions. You don’t have to do a thing; you will automatically be migrated to the new billing structure under your current subscription plan when your current subscription plan expires. <br>
<br>
New EverQuest rates as of April 25, 2002: <br>
<br>
$12.95 per Month <br>
$35.85 for 3 Months <br>
<br>
$65.70 for 6 Months <br>
